25/* dim (x,y) is defined as:
26
27 x-y if x > y
28 +0 if x <= y
29*/
30
31int
32mpfr_dim (mpfr_ptr z, mpfr_srcptr x, mpfr_srcptr y, mpfr_rnd_t rnd_mode)
33{
34 if (MPFR_IS_NAN(x) || MPFR_IS_NAN(y))
35 {
36 MPFR_SET_NAN(z);
37 MPFR_RET_NAN;
38 }
39
40 if (mpfr_cmp (x,y) > 0)
41 return mpfr_sub (z, x, y, rnd_mode);
42 else
43 {
44 MPFR_SET_ZERO(z);
45 MPFR_SET_POS(z);
46 MPFR_RET(0);
47 }
48}
